page.title: 14Kilgetty child.
page.content: I live in Kilgetty and my name is Clare Hewett. On Mondays I go dancing with Helen Brush. On Tuesdays I go to Guides and we do exciting things like going to camp. I have two brothers and we live by a forest. There used to be a tram line there and I can see the remains of coal. We used to live in Scotland but I was born in Ireland. On Friday my mum gets the Tenby Observer newspaper. There is a competition every week. I did this week's competition. It was about foods and which countries they came from.
